highlights.text: Dangrangto has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “một bài hát không vui mấy - Extended Version” is the highest at #25.
“Exit Sign” by HIEUTHUHAI and marzuz has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 198 days straight.
“Spinnin (feat. Nemzzz) - Segway Remix” by ONEFOUR, Nemzzz, and Segway is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #77.
“ZungZangZungZe” by Cheng and Han Sara is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 36 spots at #30.
